					<p class="leading-relaxed text-sm mb-3">You agree not to:</p>
					<ul class="list-none space-y-2 text-sm">
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<span class="text-terminal-amber mr-2">•</span>
							<span>Access the Service in a manner that could damage, disable, overburden, or impair the Service or interfere with any other party's use of the Service</span>
						</li>
