				</section>

				<section class="border border-terminal-green/30 p-6 bg-card">
					<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-terminal-green mb-4 font-mono">$ ./entire-agreement</h2>
					<p class="leading-relaxed text-sm">
						These Terms constitute the entire agreement between you and us
						regarding the use of the Service and supersede any prior agreements.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="border border-terminal-green/30 p-6 bg-card">
					<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-terminal-green mb-4 font-mono">$ ./refunds</h2>
					<p class="leading-relaxed text-sm mb-3">
						Money-Back Guarantee: Syntaxia may offer a money-back guarantee
