						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start">
							<span class="text-terminal-amber mr-2">•</span>
							<span>You must not be in breach of any other provision of these Terms of Service. Eligibility for the guarantee is void if you have violated any part of these Terms.</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
					<p class="leading-relaxed text-sm italic text-terminal-green/70">
						Discretionary Refunds: Outside of any specific money-back
						guarantee offered and accepted under the conditions above, certain
						refund requests may be considered by Syntaxia on a case-by-case
						basis and granted, modified, or denied at the sole discretion of
						Syntaxia.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="border border-terminal-green/30 p-6 bg-card">
					<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-terminal-green mb-4 font-mono">$ ./contact</h2>
					<p class="leading-relaxed text-sm">
						If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us at{" "}
						<a
							href="mailto:victor@syntaxia.com"
							class="text-terminal-amber hover:text-terminal-amber/80 underline"
